ZH: 我需要一个螺丝刀修理我家的椅子。
EN: I need a screwdriver to repair my chair at home.

ZH: 这颗螺丝松了，需要紧一紧。
EN: This screw is loose and needs to be tightened.

ZH: 他用力拧紧了所有的螺丝。
EN: He tightened all the screws with force.

ZH: 这个螺丝头太小，你需要一个更大的螺丝刀。
EN: The screw head is too small, you need a bigger screwdriver.

ZH: 他很快就把螺丝拧进了木板里。
EN: He quickly screwed the screw into the wooden board.

ZH: 她把螺丝拧松了，不小心把东西弄坏了。
EN: She loosened the screw and accidentally broke something.

ZH: 这个螺丝已经锈了，很难拧。
EN: This screw is rusty and hard to twist.

ZH: 我不小心把这个螺丝丢了，你有备用的吗？
EN: I accidentally lost this screw, do you have a spare one?

ZH: 善用工具可以节省很多拧螺丝的时间。
EN: Using tools wisely can save a lot of time when screwing screws.

ZH: 他用螺丝刀打开了电视机，找到了问题所在。
EN: He opened the TV with a screwdriver and found the problem.

ZH: 请小心操作，防止螺丝断裂。
EN: Please handle with care to prevent the screw from breaking.

ZH: 这里的所有螺丝都非常紧固。
EN: All the screws here are tightly fastened.

ZH: 螺丝是固定器具的常用配件。
EN: Screws are commonly used accessories for fixing objects.

ZH: 这个螺丝的形状很特别，不容易拧松。
EN: The shape of this screw is very special and not easy to loosen.

ZH: 整个机器里都充满了螺丝和螺母。
EN: The entire machine is filled with screws and nuts.

ZH: 请确保每个螺丝都拧得非常牢固。
EN: Please make sure that each screw is tightened securely.

ZH: 他很快就找到了需要的螺丝长度。
EN: He quickly found the required length of the screw.

ZH: 用榔头可以方便地把螺丝嵌入混凝土中。
EN: Using a hammer can easily embed the screws into concrete.

ZH: 这些螺丝是不锈钢的，不容易生锈。
EN: These screws are made of stainless steel and not prone to rust.

ZH: 记得在拆卸前先把螺丝保存好。
EN: Remember to keep the screws safe before disassembling.
